Tested (by me) and WORKED under these enviroments
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- Ubuntu Unity
- Ubuntu GNOME
- Ubuntu KDE
- Mint 15 Cinnamon


INSTALLATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- You can run [in terminal] the "install.sh" script and follow the instructions.
- Then you should edit the ~/.conky/cronograph_se/accuweather/forecasts.sh file
  and follow the instructions in order to type the right coordinates of your
  place/position.


